title: Pull request merge from KamalakerDadi/nilearn:surface_plotting to nilearn/nilearn:master

text:
This is pretty much ready (aside from the minor comments that I just made).

It would be useful to add a small section in the plotting chapter of the documentation: a small section 4.5 "surface plotting", that clearly uses the "versionadded" sphinx directive to stress that this is only available in nilearn 0.3.

We probably need to extend the versions of nibabel for which I did the bug fix in the tests.

⁣Sent from my phone. Please forgive brevity and mis spelling​

>What is the failure of travis ?
>
